  "instructions": [
    "Chop the tofu into small cubes. Dice the onions and peppers.",
    "Gently steam the tofu until it's cooked through but still a bit firm, about 5 minutes on medium heat.",
    "Add garlic, onion, red pepper, and wood ear mushrooms to the pan with some oil; cook for 3-4 minutes.",
    "Combine tahini sauce, soy sauce, cumin, coriander powder, salt, and pepper in a mixing bowl. Mix well until combined and smooth.",
    "Pour the sauce over the tofu and vegetables mixture and stir-fry for another minute to coat everything evenly.",
    "Serve hot with your favorite side dish."
